ent-AU14WeaponRifleTwoBore = Double-Deuce Two-Bore Rifle
    .desc = A Custom-Built Twin-Barreled Two-Bore Guage Rifle. Built to hunt the largest - or most dangerous - of game. She's Forty-Five Pounds Dry, Illegal in three Sectors, and on a hair-trigger. Take care of her, and she'll take care of you - and anything you point her at.
ent-AU14CartridgeRifleTwoBore = Rifle Cartridge (Two-Bore)
    .desc = A Two-Bore rifle cartridge. This round makes a .50 Cal look like a pea-shooter. Pray you never get hit with this thing.
